# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  Guild — Environment Variables
#  Copy this to .env and fill in your values.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Demo / Admin Identity ─────────────────────────────────────
# The wallet address that receives the seeded demo user (id=1).
DEMO_WALLET_ADDRESS=0xYOUR_WALLET_ADDRESS

# Treasury wallet — receives top-up payments.
NEXT_PUBLIC_TOPUP_TREASURY_ADDRESS=0xYOUR_TREASURY_ADDRESS
TOPUP_TREASURY_ADDRESS=0xYOUR_TREASURY_ADDRESS

# ── WalletConnect (Reown) ─────────────────────────────────────
# Get a FREE project ID at https://cloud.reown.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=

# ── Database — Turso (persistent SQLite) ─────────────────────
# Sign up free at https://turso.tech
# Leave empty → local file:data/guild.sqlite (dev only)
TURSO_DATABASE_URL=
TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=

# ── AI Compute ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Leave empty → mock mode (fake AI responses).
# Get a free key at https://openrouter.ai
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
OPENROUTER_DEFAULT_MODEL=meta-llama/llama-3.2-3b-instruct:free

# ── Storage — Crust Network (Polkadot parachain) ─────────────
# "mock"  → local dev only (no IPFS)
# "crust" → publish agent manifests to IPFS via Crust Network
STORAGE_PROVIDER=mock
CRUST_GATEWAY=https://gw.crustfiles.app
CRUST_SEED=

# ── KILT Protocol — Proof of Personhood ──────────────────────
# "mock" → dev/demo (accepts any JSON credential)
# "real" → production (verifies on Spiritnet)
KILT_VERIFY_MODE=mock
KILT_WSS_ADDRESS=wss://spiritnet.kilt.io

# ── Polkadot RPC ──────────────────────────────────────────────
POLKADOT_PEOPLE_RPC=wss://polkadot-people-rpc.polkadot.io
CRUST_RPC=wss://rpc.crust.network

# ── Payments Webhook ─────────────────────────────────────────
PAYMENTS_WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# ── Deployer (testnet only — never use for mainnet!) ─────────
DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY=

# ── Deployed Contract Addresses ──────────────────────────────
# Polkadot Hub TestNet (chain ID 420420417, native token PAS)
# Deploy: npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.ts --network polkadotHubTestnet
# Verify: npx hardhat verify --network polkadotHubTestnet <address> <constructor-args>
NEXT_PUBLIC_GUILD_CREDIT_ADDRESS=
NEXT_PUBLIC_GUILD_AGENT_ADDRESS=
NEXT_PUBLIC_GUILD_ESCROW_ADDRESS=
# Polkadot Hub MainNet (chain ID 420420419, native token DOT)
NEXT_PUBLIC_GUILD_CREDIT_ADDRESS_MAINNET=
NEXT_PUBLIC_GUILD_AGENT_ADDRESS_MAINNET=
NEXT_PUBLIC_GUILD_ESCROW_ADDRESS_MAINNET=
